snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Darktide - Announcement Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/product/EP4122-PPSA21255_00-0888672453602469

Warhammer 40,000: Darktide is coming to PS5 December 3.
Shoot, hack and slash your way through the untold horrors of the Warhammer 40,000 universe with your friends.

Pre-order and play six days early.
PlayStation Plus subscribers get up to 15% off.
